{"tid":1909763,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Quant Trading 認真分享 大跌市前既可能徵兆研究","createTime":"2020-03-04T07:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T10:20:27.000Z","uid":350019,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"47806f7df5c374df6eb8966c03279dd72dad90c2","tid":1909763,"uid":350019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"1. VIX大升<br />\n<br />\n2. 在跌市期間，全球市場之間既correlation上升。Francois Longin跟Bruno Solnik (2001) 發現correlation既改變較多跟市場方向有關，而唔係同 市場波動性有關。由此可見，correlation會傾向在熊市間上升。Simon Sosvillia-Rivero 跟 Pedro Rodriguez (2004) 研究左S&amp;P500 跟 FTSE 100 及Nikkei 225三者之間既關係，發現S&amp;P500大升或大跌時，S&amp;P500 似乎會帶領另外2個市場既走勢 走向大升 或大跌。因此，同一時間在2個市場有大損失既概率好大。<br />\n<br />\n3. Interest Rate升。值得注意一提既係：好多人認為Interest Rate升 不利股市，但銀行板塊可能係例外。從銀行商業活動角度睇，銀行往往要起愈高息環境下，先可以愈賺得多錢。因此，Interest Rate升 對銀行板塊股價走勢係好 定壞？ 唔知<br />\n<br />\n4.經濟基本面轉差。<br />\nAnnouncement type，例如：GDP, PPI, CPI, Housing Starts, New Home Sales......等等，可以幫助你了解目前經濟狀況。Fleming跟Remolona (1997)研究各項US Marco econ announcements對市場既影響力，發現Federal Funds Target Rate跟 US Non-Farm Payrolls最具影響。因此，用Fed Rate跟Non-Farm Payrolls就可以大概預測到經濟狀況。<br />\n<br />\n5.Future價格下跌/Put Option升。Fleming, Barbara Ostdeik跟Robert Whaley (1996)發現指數洐生工具既方向會帶動股票市場價格方向。Jangkoo Kang、Soonhee Lee 跟 Changjoo Lee （2004）同樣找到 南韓KOSPI 200會被 Future跟期權市場帶動。依種lead/lag relationship 同樣存在起S&amp;P500。"},{"pid":"37cb066007ab8215f94185cf2e400f03a9b1995c","tid":1909763,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"巴打睇得好全面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef86bf5fcc5a61bd4aa44050f5731f71d4a877c","tid":1909763,"uid":28668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"5好似好無謂"},{"pid":"7bcec15394e0633391688060b594a92b832ef106","tid":1909763,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"雖然完全唔明<br />\n但留返個靚名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nyoyoyo"},{"pid":"c4338f14de23d34bccdb824c57dd1d9cd1aaf9e7","tid":1909763,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:09:54.000Z","msg":"1同5大抵相同"},{"pid":"21be3ee0b48fda96db541dabd2bea4a167007237","tid":1909763,"uid":89538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"非農 今個星期五見真章"},{"pid":"af50c4e5930834b82cd5de35dceb25e8c194cf30","tid":1909763,"uid":63846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:14:38.000Z","msg":"算唔算廢話，你不如話<br />\n<br />\n6. 指數會跌"},{"pid":"4a11bf1b2868cac7a581244a39946821dcf1bbeb","tid":1909763,"uid":208228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"最基本經濟學利率下調係代表左經濟走向下坡，希望透過減息泥刺激經濟"},{"pid":"22eaa01ef7213561ce3f304edc49d24d2b83b86b","tid":1909763,"uid":208228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"Put options 我就從賭博角度出發<br />\n如果户同莊一早察覺出會有熊市既話<br />\n佢哋一定唔會再出新既低價熊証"},{"pid":"7bab74130512acecae5ee7b8922f3ebb0cb36c02","tid":1909763,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22eaa01ef7213561ce3f304edc49d24d2b83b86b","tid":1909763,"uid":208228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"Put options 我就從賭博角度出發<br />\n如果户同莊一早察覺出會有熊市既話<br />\n佢哋一定唔會再出新既低價熊証"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"market maker 佢地唔可以唔出......"},{"pid":"d22b1246f30c74f37b7d84a3b69145b2ca283488","tid":1909763,"uid":208228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bab74130512acecae5ee7b8922f3ebb0cb36c02","tid":1909763,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22eaa01ef7213561ce3f304edc49d24d2b83b86b","tid":1909763,"uid":208228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"Put options 我就從賭博角度出發<br />\n如果户同莊一早察覺出會有熊市既話<br />\n佢哋一定唔會再出新既低價熊証"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"market maker 佢地唔可以唔出......"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"咁你就睇下佢哋係點出法"},{"pid":"35576f4f6b42ae7905c77138b60eb42ccc8196ef","tid":1909763,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"第2項幾有啟發性"},{"pid":"1a310feca10a3b4e7f4708ae0b1091e795ba3cb4","tid":1909763,"uid":350019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35576f4f6b42ae7905c77138b60eb42ccc8196ef","tid":1909763,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"第2項幾有啟發性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:15:57.000Z","msg":"其實全個歐洲股市都係，唔單單英國。<br />\n值得注意既係：依到講既係correlation變化，唔係純correlation。如果 今日SPY急跌，全球最大個幾個股票市場都應該會急跌，因此correlation變化會有個peek起到"},{"pid":"ce660c8911c5edfc6e8939542ad01a0b12e7d102","tid":1909763,"uid":350019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35576f4f6b42ae7905c77138b60eb42ccc8196ef","tid":1909763,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"第2項幾有啟發性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"但另帶一提係：SPY都可以因為其他國家既股票市場被反向傳染，最簡單例子就係：阿根廷股市暴跌、希臘債務危機、墨西哥危機、俄羅斯金融危機。<br />\n<br />\n理論上該國家既股票市場市值愈細，佢一旦出現危機，對SPY影響都唔太深。依樣野都make logical sense。<br />\n<br />\n但無論如何當其他國家市場出現危機，S&amp;P500一開市 都會gap down，始終都係要realize個loss。問題係：個市場會唔會overreaction，依樣野就要試。"},{"pid":"a5b5f929ab803b6eae1dfb82a74cc439867544f0","tid":1909763,"uid":47422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得資金會流向強嘅股市例如美國令佢跌少升多<br />\n唔通舊錢真係擺喺銀行咩"},{"pid":"1edd6507673e7d0ed325216be2a03c5c62a693b5","tid":1909763,"uid":350019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5b5f929ab803b6eae1dfb82a74cc439867544f0","tid":1909763,"uid":47422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得資金會流向強嘅股市例如美國令佢跌少升多<br />\n唔通舊錢真係擺喺銀行咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T00:08:08.000Z","msg":"但都可能流入黃金、債券，甚至Long/Short equity strategy。"},{"pid":"eb278123476f1a3b87a29c22ae97d59b9c653c1e","tid":1909763,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e2b4e0fe9ba8d53003383161c28fc2b9baaacdb9","tid":1909763,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"waaaa"},{"pid":"783c721f7ce66fe8fa04e1807da4fe14a2342e3e","tid":1909763,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"廢柴一問,想問你覺得港股跌到幾多點<br />\n唔好意思我知我問得比較廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824793fc2f6592093df50357a7a9d53e8643c6dc","tid":1909763,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22eaa01ef7213561ce3f304edc49d24d2b83b86b","tid":1909763,"uid":208228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"Put options 我就從賭博角度出發<br />\n如果户同莊一早察覺出會有熊市既話<br />\n佢哋一定唔會再出新既低價熊証"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"其實好易hedge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1897133d39c796c2f675395e88be6c3a9c36cac0","tid":1909763,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"廢話"},{"pid":"ae848d96faf0e0ca696c4df71d2fdcc2b8d294c1","tid":1909763,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"而家比較想知咩徵兆代表會回升"},{"pid":"16bed8560dec27c909761a5f5b1ea8f4f58fe00a","tid":1909763,"uid":164838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"無貨係手應該點部處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a3152914ec57e581fcc35f1cc73eb0ef8ee5d4","tid":1909763,"uid":102134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"824793fc2f6592093df50357a7a9d53e8643c6dc",